# CODEOWNERS
#
# This file defines code ownership rules for GitHub.
# When a path is changed, the listed owners are automatically added as reviewers.
# Format: <path> <@username1> <@username2>
#
# ⚠️ Replace @username below with actual GitHub usernames/team names.

# ========== Default (entire codebase) ==========
*                           @project-lead @tech-lead

# ========== Governance & Docs (org-level) ==========
/GOVERNANCE.md              @project-lead @tech-lead
/CONTRIBUTING.md            @tech-lead
/SECURITY.md                @security-officer @tech-lead
/DESIGN-INTEGRATION.md      @tech-lead @design-lead
/INCIDENT-RESPONSE.md       @tech-lead @security-officer
/DEPLOYMENT.md              @tech-lead @devops-lead
/CODEOWNERS                 @project-lead @tech-lead
/README.md                  @project-lead @tech-lead

# ========== Backend (FastAPI + ldap3) ==========
/backend/                           @tech-lead @backend-maintainer
/backend/src/api/                   @tech-lead @backend-maintainer
/backend/src/api/auth.py            @tech-lead @security-officer
/backend/src/services/ldap*         @tech-lead @backend-maintainer
/backend/src/models/                @backend-maintainer
/backend/tests/                     @backend-maintainer

# ========== Frontend (React + Vite) ==========
/frontend/                          @frontend-lead @frontend-maintainer
/frontend/src/pages/                @frontend-lead @frontend-maintainer
/frontend/src/api/                  @frontend-lead @backend-maintainer
/frontend/src/components/           @frontend-maintainer

# ========== Design Previews ==========
/previews/                          @design-lead @frontend-lead
/docs/design-brief.md               @design-lead

# ========== Infrastructure ==========
/.github/                           @devops-lead @tech-lead
/scripts/                           @devops-lead @backend-maintainer
/Makefile                           @tech-lead
/pyproject.toml                     @tech-lead

# ========== ADR (Architecture Decision Records) ==========
/docs/adr/                          @tech-lead
